---
<section class="py-24 bg-neutral-off-white relative overflow-hidden">
	<!-- Grid Pattern Background (matching CyberHero style) -->
	<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-30 -z-10" style="background-image: radial-gradient(#CBD5E1 0.5px, transparent 0.5px); background-size: 24px 24px;"></div>

	<!-- Subtle gradient overlay for depth -->
	<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-blue-50/30 to-transparent -z-10"></div>

	<div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
		<!-- Section Header -->
		<div class="mb-6">
			<span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-primary-gold/10 text-primary-gold font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-6 animate-fade-in-up">
				Propuesta de Valor
			</span>
		</div>
		<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-primary-black mb-6 font-sans">
			Seguridad que <span class="text-primary-red">Impulsa Resultados</span>, No Solo los Protege
		</h2>
		<p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-4 font-sans leading-relaxed">
			La ciberseguridad estratégica reduce costos operativos hasta un <strong class="text-primary-gold">40%</strong>, acelera proyectos digitales y genera confianza que se traduce en más clientes.
		</p>
		<p class="text-base text-slate-500 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-sans">
			Nuestra propuesta: transformar la seguridad de un centro de costo a un habilitador de crecimiento medible.
		</p>

		<!-- Metrics Stats Row -->
		<div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-16">
			<!-- Stat 1 -->
			<div class="text-center p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 animate-scale-in animation-delay-200">
				<div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-primary-gold mb-2 font-sans">40%</div>
				<div class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 font-sans uppercase tracking-wide">Reducción de Incidentes</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Stat 2 -->
			<div class="text-center p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 animate-scale-in animation-delay-300">
				<div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-primary-red mb-2 font-sans">&lt;15<span class="text-2xl">min</span></div>
				<div class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 font-sans uppercase tracking-wide">Tiempo de Respuesta</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Stat 3 -->
			<div class="text-center p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 animate-scale-in animation-delay-400">
				<div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-primary-black mb-2 font-sans">3.5x</div>
				<div class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 font-sans uppercase tracking-wide">ROI Promedio</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Stat 4 -->
			<div class="text-center p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 animate-scale-in animation-delay-600">
				<div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-primary-gold mb-2 font-sans">24/7</div>
				<div class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 font-sans uppercase tracking-wide">Monitoreo Activo</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Four Value Props in 2x2 Grid -->
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
			<!-- Card 1: From Technical Jargon to Boardroom Clarity -->
			<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-lg hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-300 group animate-fade-in-up">
				<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-red-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary-black font-sans">Del Jerga Técnico a Claridad Ejecutiva</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-600 font-sans leading-relaxed">
					Transformamos hallazgos técnicos en decisiones de negocio. Su junta directiva entiende el riesgo real, no solo números de CVE.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Card 2: From Compliance Checkbox to Business Enabler -->
			<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-lg hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-300 group animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 100ms;">
				<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-amber-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary-black font-sans">De Cumplimiento a Ventaja Competitiva</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-600 font-sans leading-relaxed">
					La seguridad como habilitador de negocio. Cumplimiento sí, pero también mayor confianza de clientes y aceleración de proyectos digitales.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Card 3: From Reactive Firefighting to Proactive Resilience -->
			<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-lg hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-300 group animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 200ms;">
				<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-slate-900 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary-black font-sans">De Apagar Incendios a Construir Resiliencia</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-600 font-sans leading-relaxed">
					Respuesta proactiva, no reactiva. Reducción continua de exposición con métricas claras, no solo respuesta a incidentes.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Card 4: From Generic Reports to Tailored Business Impact -->
			<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-lg hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-300 group animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 300ms;">
				<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary-black font-sans">Riesgos Priorizados por Su Negocio</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-600 font-sans leading-relaxed">
					Análisis personalizado por impacto en SU operativa. Protegemos lo que más afecta su reputación y continuidad, no scores genéricos.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
